    <h2>Sinmag Oven Product Lines in India</h2>
    <p>Sinmag sells three core oven categories in India: deck ovens (the SM series), convection ovens (the BC/BN series), and rotary rack ovens (the ER series). Within each category, there are multiple models differentiated by capacity, energy source (gas vs electric), and feature level. Here's a full breakdown.</p>

    <h2>1. Sinmag Deck Ovens (SM Series): Full Review</h2>
    <p>Deck ovens are Sinmag's strongest product in India. The SM series covers 1-deck through 4-deck configurations, all built around a modular stacking system that lets you start with one deck and add more as production grows. Each deck chamber operates independently with its own top and bottom heat controls, and steam injection is available on most models.</p>
    <p>The construction is all-stainless exterior with high-grade firebrick decks that retain heat well and provide even bottom radiant heat. The control panel uses a digital timer and dual thermostats (top and bottom separately controllable) from 50°C to 300°C. Steam injection on the SM series is boiler-based — a proper steam tube system, not a basic water-drip — which professional bakers appreciate for consistent crust quality.</p>

