    <p>For bakeries in tier-2 or tier-3 cities, the service situation is manageable but requires planning. Most Sinmag ovens are reliable enough that service calls are infrequent — users typically report 1–2 service visits in a 5-year operating period for routine maintenance or minor issues. But if you're in a remote location, confirm with your distributor that they will service your area before buying.</p>

