      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">Sinmag vs Unox — which is better for India? <span class="icon">+</span></button>
        <div class="faq-a">Both are strong choices for Indian bakeries with different strengths. Unox excels in programmable controls, smart connectivity (the BAKERTOP platform), and premium build quality — it's the better choice for hotels, large chains, and technically sophisticated operations that can leverage advanced programming. Sinmag delivers comparable baking performance at 30–40% lower cost, which makes it better value for most commercial bakeries without advanced control requirements. Both have good service networks in major Indian cities. Our recommendation: if you'll actively use the smart features, Unox is worth the premium. If you just need a reliable oven that bakes well and lasts, Sinmag gives better value.</div>
